      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver or a long-distance commuter. The interior is clean and shows minimal wear, while the exterior remains in great shape despite a few minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with normal use. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
