    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. It has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior and an interior that still has that new-car smell. Every feature functions perfectly, and there are no mechanical issues or cosmetic blemishes whatsoever. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in pristine, collector-grade condition.",
